<Layout title="CPF for Foreigners: What EP & S Pass Holders Need to Know | SalaryCalculator.sg" description="Complete guide to CPF rules for foreigners in Singapore. Covers Employment Pass, S Pass, and Work Permit holders - exemptions, levies, and take-home pay impact.">
